quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,(Aey nabi) Apne Rubb-e-bartar kay naam ki tasbeeh karo
  87,2,Jisne paida kiya aur tanasub qayam kiya (then proportioned it)
  87,3,Jisne taqdeer banayi phir raah dikhayi
  87,4,Jisne nabataat(pasture) ugayi
  87,5,Phir unko siyah kuda karkat bana diya
  87,6,Hum tumhey padhwa dengey phir tum nahin bhuloge
  87,7,Siwaye uske jo Allah chahey.Woh zahir ko bhi jaanta hai aur jo kuch posheeda(hidden) hai usko bhi
  87,8,Aur hum tumhein aasaan tarikey ki sahoolat dete hain
  87,9,lihaza tum naseehat karo agar naseehat nafey(faiydamand) ho
  87,10,Jo shaks darta hai wo naseehat qabool karlega
  87,11,Aur ussey guraiz karega woh intehayi bad-bakht
  87,12,Jo badi aag mei jayega
  87,13,phir na usmein marega aur na jiyega
  87,14,Falah paa gaya woh jisne pakizgi ikhtiyar ki
  87,15,Aur apne Rubb ka naam yaad kiya phir namaz padhi
  87,16,Magar tumlog duniya ki zindagi ko tarjeeh detay ho
  87,17,halaanke aakhirat behtar hai aur baqi rehne wali hai
  87,18,Yahi baat pehle aaey huey saheefon(scriptures) mei bhi kahi gayi thi
  87,19,Ibrahim aur Moosa ke saheefon mein